# Changelog V.0.0.20

## Major Changes

- License updated to GNU General Public License v3.0 License from MIT License and the license file was updated to reflect the change.
- The `README.md` file was updated to reflect the license change and the license section was added to the end of the file and rhe compilaton section was move to the `COMPILING.md` file
- Updated dependancies with "cargo update" command
- New Nightly Build with GitHub application
- Fix and added correct dimensions for the Unix like system
- Added Helper script and cargo makefile support
- Added more dimensions for icons
- Added ASCII mime type icons for Unix like system
- Better Versions scheme for the alpha: only use 3 letters and increment to 10 when there it is a major version.
- Updated the Code Of Respect to the latest version
- Arch Package now follow the linux/unix File system hierachy and XDG sepcs with addded locales and examples ascii files
- Now show the release type with the --version or -v command line flag
- Fix the Windows ascii icon to show the correct one and add it to Linux
- Update Desktop Entry

## Minor Changes

- Betters functions names
- Some Cleaning and refactor of the code
- Better Codebase
- Mores Translation Texts and fix the help string not being translated
- update the gitignore so it work with the reorganisation of the arch packages folder

## Big fixes

- Fix the desktop file
- Update the copyright date
- fix the rtf documentations
- make install.sh executable
- fix the Windows Build Manifest

